## Gate B Purpose
<!-- Gate B authorises closure of Phase 2 and transition to Phase 3 (System Design). -->
Gate B validates that all Phase 2 requirements artefacts are complete, internally consistent,
and traceable. The frozen requirements baseline becomes the authoritative input for Phase 3 design.

